/// Records Power BI embedded report usage events collected from PostHog across all CRM client instances. Each row represents a unique combination of user, date, and report, containing both the number of sessions and the number of events generated within those sessions. Used for Power BI adoption analysis, report engagement tracking, and embedded dashboard usage monitoring across client deployments.
table 'PostHog Power BI Usage Events'
	lineageTag: 3241599c-9426-4301-9c7f-d2aedfcd587e

